data.name: size
data.description: It is a multiplier to the current font size to determine the icon's dimensions. A value of 1 renders the icon at the same size (1em) as the surrounding text.

data.name: viewBox
data.description: Sets the viewBox size of the icon.

data.name: focusable
data.description: Indicating whether the icon should be focusable via keyboard navigation.

data.name: stroke
data.description: When set, it changes the icon's styling from filled to stroked, rendering the icon as an outline.
